1
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:10,320
Leng Yue got hurt for saving me.

2
00:00:10,320 --> 00:00:13,080
General Xiao arrived at that time.

3
00:00:15,790 --> 00:00:19,659
His Highness found fake copper cash in the pay of General Xiao.

4
00:00:19,660 --> 00:00:23,419
His Highness said Prefect Li Zhang might play a role.

5
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:27,319
Lord Jing and His Highness made a bet and went to the county government.

6
00:00:27,319 --> 00:00:29,739
I took His Highness and General Xiao home.

7
00:00:29,740 --> 00:00:32,650
My brother met us.

8
00:00:33,380 --> 00:00:35,089
He scolded me for that.

9
00:00:35,089 --> 00:00:36,379
He's really ill-tempered.

10
00:00:36,380 --> 00:00:38,040
I can't do anything about that.

11
00:00:41,410 --> 00:00:44,379
Sir, would you please do me a favor?

12
00:00:44,380 --> 00:00:46,589
We'd love to. What's it?

13
00:00:46,590 --> 00:00:48,199
It's late now.

14
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:52,820
Will you allow us to stay here for one night?

15
00:00:53,470 --> 00:00:55,070
Are you serious?

16
00:00:55,760 --> 00:00:57,729
Stay here?

17
00:00:57,729 --> 00:01:01,319
Sir, we are a family of coroners.

18
00:01:01,319 --> 00:01:05,429
Even the villagers dislike getting in contact with us

19
00:01:05,430 --> 00:01:07,809
because they think it's unlucky.

20
00:01:07,809 --> 00:01:10,710
Will you really stay here?

21
00:01:12,650 --> 00:01:16,609
As a coroner, you are helping the dead and the government.

22
00:01:16,609 --> 00:01:18,429
How could it be unlucky?

23
00:01:18,430 --> 00:01:20,979
Every government office has its mortuary.

24
00:01:20,980 --> 00:01:25,650
Chu Chu saw that there're also such rooms in my home in Chang'an.

25
00:01:25,650 --> 00:01:27,850
If you have to say so,

26
00:01:27,850 --> 00:01:31,109
I'm about the same as you are.

27
00:01:31,110 --> 00:01:34,069
You have such a room, too?

28
00:01:34,070 --> 00:01:35,399
Yes, they really have one.

29
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:38,000
I even performed an autopsy there.

30
00:01:38,750 --> 00:01:41,309
Autopsy results are the basis for investigation.

31
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:43,899
One false step will make a great difference.

32
00:01:43,900 --> 00:01:47,109
As a judge, we have to be cautious.

33
00:01:47,110 --> 00:01:50,670
Go tidy up a room and prepare some dishes and wine.

34
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:53,419
You don't know where the wine is.

35
00:01:53,419 --> 00:01:55,429
I store them. I know where it is.

36
00:01:55,430 --> 00:01:57,230
I will go take it.

37
00:01:58,270 --> 00:01:59,870
Come with me.

38
00:02:03,650 --> 00:02:04,729
Zhang Yun. Chen Feng.

39
00:02:04,729 --> 00:02:05,469
- Yes.
- Yes.

40
00:02:05,469 --> 00:02:08,959
Go visit Jing Yi and tell him I'm staying here tonight.

41
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:11,429
Ask him to do whatever he should do. He doesn't need to wait for me.

42
00:02:11,429 --> 00:02:13,070
- Yes.
- Yes.

