[Episode 11]

46
00:03:49,470 --> 00:03:51,699
Brother, what's the matter?

47
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:53,959
Tell me who those people are.

48
00:03:53,959 --> 00:03:55,579
You heard that.

49
00:03:55,580 --> 00:03:58,179
One is a judge from the imperial court.

50
00:03:58,180 --> 00:04:01,339
The other is his elder brother, a general.

51
00:04:01,340 --> 00:04:03,119
His men once suppressed bandits around here.

52
00:04:03,119 --> 00:04:04,859
Every word is true.

53
00:04:04,860 --> 00:04:06,299
You went to Chang'an alone.

54
00:04:06,300 --> 00:04:07,869
How could you know people like that?

55
00:04:07,869 --> 00:04:09,340
I met them on the exam.

56
00:04:09,340 --> 00:04:11,269
You went their house on the exam?

57
00:04:11,269 --> 00:04:13,919
I've been helping him investigate when I was in Chang'an.

58
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:17,380
So he let me stay so that he could ask for information.

59
00:04:17,380 --> 00:04:19,539
You even lived in his house?

60
00:04:19,540 --> 00:04:22,019
Jing Yi should hold Li Zhang for half a day.

61
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:25,339
We will meet him in the government office after we have supper.

62
00:04:25,339 --> 00:04:27,360
Why do you want to stay here now?

63
00:04:28,230 --> 00:04:29,619
Isn't it odd?

64
00:04:29,619 --> 00:04:33,940
Chu Chu isn't treated as she's a biological daughter.

65
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:37,179
They are all good to her, aren't they?

66
00:04:37,179 --> 00:04:39,220
Yes, they are good to her.

67
00:04:39,220 --> 00:04:40,869
But it's weird.

68
00:04:40,869 --> 00:04:41,999
Weird?

69
00:04:41,999 --> 00:04:45,629
As her father, Chu Ping shows his love.

70
00:04:45,630 --> 00:04:47,789
But it's in a polite way.

71
00:04:47,790 --> 00:04:49,490
Polite?

72
00:04:50,420 --> 00:04:52,819
I once left the capital for a case.

73
00:04:52,820 --> 00:04:54,699
Mother was worrying all night.

74
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:57,560
When I went for her for some tea,

75
00:04:57,560 --> 00:05:00,669
she said in anger she wouldn't allow me to drink.

76
00:05:00,670 --> 00:05:04,159
Chu Chu has left home for so long without any news.

77
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,529
Now she's back all of a sudden.

78
00:05:05,530 --> 00:05:07,969
But Chu Ping didn't blame her at all.

79
00:05:07,970 --> 00:05:12,190
Maybe it's because Chu Ping isn't as bad-tempered as Mother.

80
00:05:12,190 --> 00:05:14,089
No.

81
00:05:14,090 --> 00:05:19,250
And Chu He, he didn't act like an elder brother.

82
00:05:20,130 --> 00:05:22,059
Chu He is a bit weird.

83
00:05:22,059 --> 00:05:25,669
If you were sent back by others after being away home for a long time,

84
00:05:25,669 --> 00:05:27,809
I'd first see if you are all right.

85
00:05:27,810 --> 00:05:31,649
As long as you are fine and the visitors aren't malicious,

86
00:05:31,650 --> 00:05:33,999
I'd say thanks of course.

87
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,699
But Chu He didn't.

88
00:05:35,699 --> 00:05:38,849
It seems the kinder we are, the more he cares about who we are

89
00:05:38,849 --> 00:05:41,040
and the more malicious he is.

90
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,099
You are right.

91
00:05:43,099 --> 00:05:45,151
As a girl with an unimpeachable reputation,

92
00:05:45,151 --> 00:05:47,809
how could you just live in a strange man's house at random?

93
00:05:47,810 --> 00:05:49,469
You don't know what intentions he had.

94
00:05:49,469 --> 00:05:51,700
He had good intentions.

95
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,859
You know what?

96
00:05:53,859 --> 00:05:56,819
I lost my purse then and was wronged by others.

97
00:05:56,819 --> 00:05:59,599
He caught the thief and got my purse back.

98
00:05:59,599 --> 00:06:02,859
When I was hijacked in the street, he arranged his men to save me.

99
00:06:02,859 --> 00:06:05,699
What's more, he has never looked down upon me.

100
00:06:05,699 --> 00:06:08,999
He said I'm the best coroner he has ever met.

101
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:12,969
I failed the last test for coroner, but he is willing to give me another chance.

102
00:06:12,969 --> 00:06:17,299
He said he'd take me back to Chang'an if he agreed to take me on.

103
00:06:17,299 --> 00:06:21,219
Even if he decides not to hire me, he will investigate my background

104
00:06:21,219 --> 00:06:24,939
so as to rank me as a coroner.

105
00:06:24,939 --> 00:06:27,400
He even wants to investigate your background?

106
00:06:28,090 --> 00:06:31,179
Brother, it's an item in the ranking test.

107
00:06:31,179 --> 00:06:33,370
You took it in your first test, right?

108
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,939
Yes, that's true.

109
00:06:35,939 --> 00:06:40,639
I know others said I was born out of wedlock.

110
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:42,969
But you've asked me to ignore the words since I was a little girl.

111
00:06:42,970 --> 00:06:44,619
You told me that's nonsense.

112
00:06:44,619 --> 00:06:47,729
He's the smartest and fairest person I've ever seen.

113
00:06:47,729 --> 00:06:49,729
He won't trust the nonsense readily.

114
00:06:49,729 --> 00:06:52,440
He will figure it out himself.

115
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:55,689
Lass, do you have to be the coroner?

116
00:06:55,690 --> 00:06:57,629
Our family are all coroners for generations.

117
00:06:57,629 --> 00:06:59,719
I'm one of us. Of course, I will be a coroner.

118
00:06:59,719 --> 00:07:01,230
This...

119
00:07:04,020 --> 00:07:07,910
If the Handsome Judge doesn't exist,

120
00:07:07,910 --> 00:07:12,689
the coroner around him should be the one making people jealous.

121
00:07:12,690 --> 00:07:17,679
I thought he sent me home because he didn't want me.

122
00:07:17,679 --> 00:07:19,629
But he is staying for one night.

123
00:07:19,629 --> 00:07:21,119
It means I still have a chance.

124
00:07:21,119 --> 00:07:24,100
That's my last chance. I will surely take the opportunity.

125
00:07:24,100 --> 00:07:26,499
You want to leave home so much to work with him?

126
00:07:26,499 --> 00:07:27,639
Of course not.

127
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:31,440
After I make some achievements, I will take you all to Chang'an.

128
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:35,979
Brother, Chang'an is big, very beautiful.

129
00:07:35,979 --> 00:07:37,529
It has everything.

130
00:07:37,530 --> 00:07:39,019
You will like it.

131
00:07:39,019 --> 00:07:40,820
I don't like it.

132
00:07:49,420 --> 00:07:51,769
You talked to me about our father.

133
00:07:51,769 --> 00:07:54,519
So you doubt it's related to the Chu family?

134
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:57,639
The Chu family and Father were close.

135
00:07:57,639 --> 00:08:00,289
There must be clues about Father here.

136
00:08:00,290 --> 00:08:02,599
The Chu family hide Chu Chu's background on purpose

137
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:04,840
and Chu Chu hides the history of the pendant deliberately.

138
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:09,189
We can only find out the truth here.

139
00:08:09,189 --> 00:08:13,410
Are you sure the witch doctor is our father?

140
00:08:14,690 --> 00:08:16,810
That's the only possibility.

141
00:08:18,530 --> 00:08:20,409
The Chu family are honest people.

142
00:08:20,410 --> 00:08:23,409
How about asking them straightly?

143
00:08:23,410 --> 00:08:25,210
It's not the time.

144
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:27,939
Okay. It's up to you.

145
00:08:27,939 --> 00:08:31,439
Will you ask some guardsmen here?

146
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:33,089
Or I call some soldiers?

147
00:08:33,090 --> 00:08:36,080
Otherwise, you will live with me tonight.

148
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:44,189
Excuse me.

149
00:08:44,189 --> 00:08:45,399
It's the backlands here.

150
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:48,409
Our family lives here alone without any relative visiting.

151
00:08:48,410 --> 00:08:50,119
We don't have many rooms.

152
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:52,980
Today we can get only one room for you.

153
00:08:52,980 --> 00:08:54,559
It's fine. That's enough.

154
00:08:54,559 --> 00:08:56,779
My brother and I haven't been together for long.

155
00:08:56,779 --> 00:08:58,169
Right?

156
00:08:58,170 --> 00:08:59,799
Thank you for understanding.

157
00:08:59,799 --> 00:09:01,070
Thank you.

158
00:09:01,070 --> 00:09:03,320
I have to leave now.

159
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,800
Let's go.

