180
00:10:19,409 --> 00:10:21,090
Father, here's the liquor.

181
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:25,389
You silly boy. Why are you standing here?

182
00:10:25,389 --> 00:10:27,780
Serve the liquor to the guests.

183
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:36,989
